      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Numerical solver verification against canonical pipe flow benchmark",
      "description": "ANSYS Fluent v2023R1 verified against Poiseuille flow analytical solution and lid-driven cavity benchmark (Re=1000). Velocity field L2 error norms of 0.31% and 1.2% respectively, confirming correct solver implementation for laminar and transitional regimes relevant to CPB pump operation.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
