        "type": "UncertaintyQuantification",
        "method": "Analytical benchmark comparison",
        "description": "L2 error norm computed between CFD solution and analytical Poiseuille velocity profile across 12 cross-sectional measurement planes. Maximum pointwise error 0.8%, L2 norm 0.31%. Lid-driven cavity comparison against Ghia et al. (1982) reference data.",
