        "type": "UncertaintyQuantification",
        "method": "Multi-model ensemble comparison",
        "description": "Turbulence model-form uncertainty estimated as half-range of NIH predictions across three calibrated turbulence models. Uncertainty contribution ±12% of mean NIH value. Combined with discretization uncertainty (3.2%) using RSS: total numerical uncertainty ±12.4%.",
