      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v2023R1 used under institutional software license management. Version recorded in simulation metadata. Standard solver regression test suite executed prior to study; all 47 benchmark cases passed. Installation qualification documentation archived in project repository per institutional SOP-CFD-001."
